destiny%20and%20have%20that%20direct%20relationship%20with%20users.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%222ab8fe61-ef2a-4b87-89de-ada512922bc1%5C%22%3Eio%20vs%20IO%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20writing%20this%20from%20Google%20IO%2C%20the%20internet%20giant's%20annual%20conference.%20Altman%20loves%20to%20crash%20this%20party.%20He%20did%20it%20last%20year%2C%20and%20he's%20doing%20it%20again%20today.%20It's%20all%20the%20more%20perfect%20because%20Ive's%20device%20company%20is%20called%20io.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20interpretation%20of%20this%20party-crashing%20is%20that%20Altman%20could%20be%20pretty%20worried%20about%20Google.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20that%20very%20expensive%20deal%20with%20Apple%2C%20Google%20is%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdoj-attack-google-search-distribution-monopoly-worries-investors-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emaster%20of%20distribution%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20it's%20using%20everything%20at%20its%20disposal%20to%20quickly%20get%20its%20new%20AI%20products%20and%20tools%20into%20as%20many%20hands%20as%20possible.%20These%20are%20the%20offerings%20that%20compete%20directly%20with%20ChatGPT.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere%20are%20some%20examples%20of%20Google's%20distribution%20power%2C%20taken%20partly%20from%20this%20week%20at%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-cofounder-sergey-brin-ai-io-conference%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EGoogle%20IO%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20partly%20from%20all%20the%20work%20Google%20has%20been%20doing%20for%20the%20past%2020%20years%20or%20so.%20For%20a%20startup%20like%20OpenAI%2C%20this%20must%20be%20terrifying.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EAndroid%2C%20Google's%20mobile%20operating%20system%2C%20supports%20more%20than%203%20billion%20devices.%20The%20company%20is%20prominently%20displaying%20its%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-ai-gemini-bard%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EGemini%20AI%3C%2Fa%3E%20chatbot%20service%20on%20as%20m