%2Fdonald-trump%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPresident%20Donald%20Trump's%3C%2Fa%3E%20key%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-no-tax-on-tips-las-vegas-hospitality-restaurants-hotels-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ecampaign%20promises%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20fact%2C%20lawmakers%20on%20both%20sides%20of%20the%20aisle%20are%20surprised%20that%20the%20%26quot%3BNo%20Tax%20on%20Tips%20Act%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20bipartisan%20bill%20sponsored%20by%20Republican%20Sen.%20Ted%20Cruz%20of%20Texas%20and%20Democratic%20Sen.%20Jacky%20Rosen%20of%20Nevada%2C%20passed%20at%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20a%20little%20amazed%20the%20Democrats%20didn't%20block%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Cruz%20told%20BI.%20%26quot%3BBut%20I'll%20take%20yes%20for%20an%20answer.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20it%20turns%20out%2C%20Cruz's%20surprise%20is%20warranted.%20While%20no%20Democratic%20senators%20said%20they%20were%20outright%20opposed%2C%20several%20told%20BI%20on%20Wednesday%20that%20they%20still%20had%20questions%20or%20concerns%20about%20the%20idea%2C%20or%20were%20simply%20ambivalent%20about%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat's%20one%20way%20to%20approach%20the%20topic%2C%26quot%3B%20Democratic%20Sen.%20Tim%20Kaine%20of%20Virginia.%20%26quot%3BThe%20other%20way%20is%20to%20raise%20the%20minimum%20wage%2C%20and%20sort%20of%20eliminate%20a%20tip-based%20economy%2C%20which%20is%20what%20a%20lot%20of%20countries%20do.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20obviously%20great%20for%20people%20who%20make%20their%20incomes%20off%20of%20tips.%20It's%20just%20a%20question%20of%20fairness%2C%26quot%3B%20Democratic%20Sen.%20Chris%20Murphy%20of%20Connecticut%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt%20just%2C%20on%20its%20own%2C%20seems%20to%20be%20a%20little%20strange%20to%20decide%20that%20certain%20workers%20are%20getting%20taxed%20at%20a%20rate%20that's%20much%20less%20than%20other%20workers.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20bill%20passed%20on%20Tuesday%20night