ity%20and%20entertainment%20industry%20in%20cities%20like%20Las%20Vegas.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20senator%20also%20wanted%20to%20divorce%20the%20issue%20from%20the%20GOP's%20broader%20bill%2C%20which%20includes%20safety-net%20cuts%20that%20Democrats%20oppose.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20office%20ran%20a%20hotline%20on%20both%20sides%20of%20the%20aisle%20and%2C%20after%20seeing%20no%20objections%2C%20Senator%20Rosen%20went%20to%20the%20floor%20to%20pass%20this%20bipartisan%20bill%20by%20itself%20and%20without%20any%20poison%20pills%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20spokesperson%20for%20Rosen%20told%20BI.%20%26quot%3BIn%20doing%20so%2C%20Senate%20Democrats%20are%20showing%20we%20can%20deliver%20tax%20relief%20for%20working-class%20families%20without%20Republicans'%20extreme%20cuts%20to%20Medicaid%20and%20SNAP.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221777%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Democratic%20Sens.%20Jacky%20Rosen%20and%20Catherine%20Cortez%20Masto%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F682e202868a292900801f39a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221333%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDemocratic%20Sens.%20Jacky%20Rosen%20and%20Catherine%20Cortez%20Masto%20both%20support%20the%20bill%2C%20owing%20to%20Nevada's%20concentration%20of%20tipped%20workers.%3Cp%3EAndrew%20Caballero-Reynolds%20%2F%20AFP%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ESenate%20Minority%20Leader%20Chuck%20Schumer%20applauded%20the%20passage%20of%20the%20bill%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20saying%20in%20a%20statement%20that%20%26quot%3Bthanks%20to%20Senator%20Rosen's%20incredible%20leadership%2C%20we%20are%20one%20step%20closer%20to%20eliminating%20taxes%20on%20tipped%20wages%20for%20hardworking%20Americans.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20while%20the%20bill%20has%20the%20support%20of%20Republicans%20and%20Nevada's%20other%20Democratic%20senator%2C%20Catherine%20Cortez%20Masto%2C%20none%20of%20the%20Democratic%20senators%20who%20BI%20spoke%20with%20on%20Wednes