.%20Four%20other%20firms%20targeted%20with%20orders%20that%20threatened%20their%20client%20relationships%20have%20since%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbig-law-fight-trump-perkins-coie-jenner-block-wilmer-hale-susman-godfrey-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewon%20legal%20victories%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20month%2C%20members%20of%20Congress%20led%20by%20Rep.%20David%20Min%20and%20Rep.%20April%20McClain%20Delaney%20asked%20the%20firms%20that%20cut%20deals%20to%20repudiate%20them%2C%20calling%20them%20unethical%20and%20illegal.%20Critics%20of%20the%20deals%20say%20the%20vague%20commitments%20don't%20square%20with%20the%20firms'%20obligations%20to%20exercise%20independent%20professional%20judgment%20and%20provide%20legal%20help%20for%20the%20needy%20rather%20than%20the%20politically%20connected.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMin%20told%20Business%20Insider%20he%20disagreed%20with%20the%20law%20firms'%20responses%20and%20said%20he%20and%20other%20Congressional%20Democrats%20were%20considering%20their%20next%20steps.%20He%20said%20the%20law%20firms%20might%20have%20violated%20state%20laws%20as%20well%20as%20federal%20laws%2C%20and%20said%20investigations%20and%20enforcement%20activities%20could%20take%20place%20in%20other%20jurisdictions%20%E2%80%94%20or%20once%20Democrats%20take%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20probably%20incumbent%20on%20state%20and%20local%20and%20federal%2C%20should%20that%20time%20arise%2C%20authorities%20to%20investigate%20these%20settlements%2C%26quot%3B%20Min%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20law%20firms%20%26quot%3Bcan%20disavow%20the%20agreements%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%20%26quot%3BIf%20they%20don't%20do%20that%20and%20continue%20to%20perform%20%E2%80%94%20for%20example%2C%20if%20they%20decide%20to%20represent%20January%206%20protesters%E2%80%A6%20then%20I%20think%20you%20have%20very%20clearly%20a%20circumstance%20where%20they%20violated%20a%20number%20of%20laws.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20sta