as%20a%20drain%20built%20into%20the%20bottom%20so%20you%20can%20let%20out%20any%20spilled%20beverages%20or%20ice%20melt%20without%20dumping%20the%20entire%20contents%2C%20but%20for%20the%20record%2C%20there%20won't%20be%20much%20meltwater%20provided%20you%20keep%20the%20lid%20secure%20most%20of%20the%20time.%20This%20cooler%20offers%20three-day%20ice%20retention%20even%20when%20the%20mercury%20tops%2090%20degrees%20Fahrenheit.%20Oh%2C%20and%20this%20cooler%20is%20made%20in%20America%2C%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22bea1078c-9a8a-4ae6-a6a5-ba3e8da58b59%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Best%20backpack%5C%22%3EBest%20backpack%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20should%20be%20no%20surprise%20that%20Yeti%20appears%20multiple%20times%20in%20this%20guide.%20The%20company%20has%20made%20its%20name%20manufacturing%20some%20of%20the%20best%20coolers%20on%20the%20market.%20With%20its%20Hopper%20M20%2C%20the%20brand%20delivers%20the%20same%20durable%20construction%20and%20quality%20design%20its%20fans%20have%20come%20to%20expect%20in%20a%20backpack%20cooler.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20space%20enough%20to%20carry%20roughly%2020%20cans%20of%20beer%20or%20soda%20(with%20ice%20included)%2C%20or%2025%20pounds%20of%20ice%2C%20the%20Hopper%20M20%20is%20at%20no%20lack%20of%20available%20cooler%20space.%20And%20don't%20worry%20about%20the%20loaded%20pack%20feeling%20especially%20heavy%2C%20either.%20Yeti%20designed%20it%20so%20weight%20distributes%20evenly%2C%20and%20its%20ergonomic%20shoulder%20straps%20make%20it%20comfortable%20to%20tote%20around%2C%20whether%20it's%20down%20a%20long%20trail%20to%20the%20beach%2C%20a%20short%20jaunt%20to%20a%20campsite%2C%20or%20a%20few%20steps%20to%20a%20backyard.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYeti%20also%20includes%20its%20Magshield%20zippers%2C%20which%20help%20keep%20any%20contents%20from%20spilling%20out%20(e.g.%2C%20water%20from%20melted%20ice)%2C%20and%20its%20ColdCell%20Insulation%2C%20which%20can%20keep%20ice%20for%20several%20days%20(something%20we've%20tested%20and%20confirmed%20often).%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESimilar%20to%20many%20of%20Yeti's%20products%2C%20the%20Hopper%20M20%20isn't%20cheap%2C%20sporting%20a%20price%20tag%20of%20%24325.%20However%2C%20Yeti%20consistently%20exceeds%20standards%20of%20quality%2C%20and%20this%20backpack%20cooler%20is%20no%20different%20%E2%80%94%20it'll%20be%20one%20of%20your%20favorite%20pieces%20of%20go-to%20gear%20for%20several%2C%20several%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%228321ef1b-99d4-41c3-99d9-db4487b7a628%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Best%20soft%5C%22%3EBest%20soft%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20should%20be%20apparent%20at%20this%20point%20that%20Yeti's%20coolers%20are%20worth%20every%20bit%20of%20the%20recognition%20of%20nabbing%20three%20spots%20in%20this%20guide%2C%20as%20its%20coolers%20are%20just%C2%A0%3Cem%3Ethat%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3Edamn%20good.%20And%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20picking%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fkitchen%2Fbest-soft-cooler%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ebest%20soft%20cooler%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20Hopper%20M30%20is%20a%20clear%20choice.%20With%20the%20brand's%20patented%20bomb-proof%20construction%2C%20some%20impressive%20ice%20retention%2C%20and%20surprisingly%20large%20capacity%2C%20this%20is%20the%20one%20you%20want%20for%20day%20trips%20to%20the%20beach%20or%20local%20park.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20the%20Hopper%20M30%20gets%20a%20lot%20right%2C%20its%20best%20feature%20is%20how%20well%20it%20keeps%20ice%20throughout%20the%20day.%20During%20my%20tests%2C%20it%20reliably%20kept%20ice%20anywhere%20from%20roughly%2015%20hours%20up%20to%2020%20hours%2C%20depending%20on%20how%20hot%20it%20was%20outside%2C%20how%20often%20I%20opened%20it%20for%20a%20drink%2C%20and%20whether%20I'd%20remember%20to%20fully%20zip%20it%20up%20or%20not.%20But%20even%20on%20its%20lower%2015-hour%20days%2C%20that's%20more%20than%20enough%20time%20to%20get%20your%20fill%20of%20hanging%20at%20the%20park%20or%20lounging%20on%20the%20beach%20(it%20was%20even%20a%20nice%20supplemental%20cooler%20on%20two-day%20car%20camping%20trips).%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou'll%20be%20surprised%20at%20how%20much%20this%20cooler%20is%20able%20to%20house%2C%20too.%20Despite%20often%20stocking%20it%20with%20more%20cans%20of%20beer%20than%20I'd%20know%20what%20to%20do%20with%2C%20there%20was%20still%20plenty%20of%20room%20for%20a%20couple%20of%20sandwiches%2C%20some%20cheese%20sticks%2C%20and%20whatever%20other%20snacks%20seemed%20fit%20for%20the%20outing.%20It%20also%20comes%20with%20a%20padded%20shoulder%20strap%20that%20makes%20lugging%20the%20thing%20either%20from%20the%20car%20to%20the%20beach%20or%20park%20a%20comfortable%20experience%20%E2%80%94%20I've%20even%20slung%20it%20over%20my%20shoulder%20while%20riding%20my%20bike%2C%20and%20it%20was%20completely%20fine.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%20there's%20its%20durability.%20The%20Hopper%20M30%20can%20take%20an%20utter%20beating%2C%20whether%20it's%20getting%20tossed%20into%20the%20back%20of%20a%20car%2C%20dragged%20down%20a%20trail%2C%20or%20even%20falling%20completely%20off%20my%20bike%20(this%20only%20happened%20once%20and%20the%20cooler%20managed%20to%20avoid%20taking%20any%20damage%20at%20all).%20Its%20zipper%20closure%20system%20also%20seals%20the%20cooler%20airtight%2C%20and%20not%20even%20water%20drips%20out%20if%20it's%20tilted%20upside%20down%20or%20lying%20on%20its%20side.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou'd%20be%20hard-pressed%20to%20find%20a%20more%20high-quality%20soft%20cooler%2C%20which%20is%20why%20the%20Hopper%20M30%20is%20our%20go-to%20whenever%20I%20want%20to%20leave%20my%20bulky%2C%20cumbersome%20cooler%20at%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ae2bad15-3357-4972-aac3-66919fd480b6%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Best%20budget%20soft%5C%22%3EBest%20budget%20soft%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20don't%20need%20to%20spend%20a%20fortune%20to%20buy%20an%20effective%20soft%20cooler%20for%20general%20use%20and%2C%20in%20fact%2C%20this%20is%20one%20of%20the%20coolers%20I%20tend%20to%20use%20most.%20From%20lighter%20fishing%20excursions%20to%20an%20afternoon%20picnic%2C%20I%20haven't%20found%20a%20handier%20cooler%2C%20hands%20down.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20also%20been%20using%20it%20for%20well%20over%20two%20years%20%E2%80%94%20that's%20two%20years%20of%20sea%20time%2C%20being%20left%20outside%20through%20every%20season%2C%20and%20countless%20fruitful%20trips%20home%20from%20the%20fishing%20grounds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22the%20AO%20Carbon%20Soft%20Cooler%20on%20a%20picnic%20table%20outside%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6149fff1de0e7b00194b94fe%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EOwen%20Burke%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20brand%20touts%20its%20use%20of%20high-density%20insulation%2C%20it%20seems%20to%20be%20that%20the%20large%20air%20pockets%20between%20the%20insulation%20and%20the%20inner%20and%20outer%20linings%20are%20what%20give%20it%20its%20best%20retention%20qualities.%20High-density%20foam%20(or%20insulation)%20is%20actually%20a%20better%20conductor%20of%20heat%20than%20low-density%20foam%20(or%20insulation)%2C%20while%20air%20is%20one%20of%20the%20worst%20conductors.%20So%2C%20while%20the%20insulation%20may%20seem%20curiously%20loose%20against%20the%20linings%2C%20all%20that%20space%20is%20actually%20helping%20to%20improve%20ice%20and%20temperature%20retention.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERegarding%20features%2C%20there%20are%20more%20than%20you'd%20find%20in%20your%20average%20soft%20cooler.%20First%2C%20there%20are%20briefcase-style%20handles%20that%20velcro%20together%20and%20a%20padded%20shoulder%20sling%2C%20buckles%20on%20either%20end%20for%20strapping%20it%20down%20and%20making%20it%20more%20compact%2C%20and%20there's%20also%20an%20outside%20zipper%20pouch%20in%20which%20I%20keep%20utensils%2C%20a%20cutting%20board%2C%20a%20folded%20rag%2C%20a%20wine%20key%2C%20and%20still%20have%20room%20for%20a%20couple%20of%20other%20odds%20and%20ends.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20only%20room%20for%20improvement%20with%20this%20cooler%20is%20an%20airtight%20zipper%20but%20that%20would%20probably%20drive%20the%20cost%20up%20too%20much.%20It's%20also%20a%20bit%20tougher%20to%20clean%20than%20some%20other%20options%20in%20this%20guide%2C%20but%20it's%20nothing%20a%20sponge%20and%20some%20dish%20soap%20can't%20handle%20(I%20like%20to%20fill%20it%20with%20warm%20soapy%20water%2C%20zip%20it%2C%20and%20give%20it%20a%20shake%20first).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%229688fa66-0aa7-46db-84ee-a1bf05b00663%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22How%20we%20test%20coolers%5C%22%3EHow%20we%20test%20coolers%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22All%20of%20the%2011%20coolers%20we%20tested%20lined%20up%20in%20a%20fenced%20in%20backyard%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F614a0027de0e7b00194b9513%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EOwen%20Burke%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EEach%20cooler%20featured%20in%20this%20guide%20went%20through%20several%20field%20tests%2C%20be%20it%20fishing%2C%20camping%2C%20lounging%20in%20the%20backyard%20at%20home%2C%20or%20at%20the%20park%2C%20to%20see%20how%20well%20they%20fared%20across%20these%20four%20categories%3A%C2%A0ice%20retention%2C%20durability%2C%20portability%2C%C2%A0and%C2%A0value.%20Specifically%2C%20here's%20how%20each%20category%20factored%20into%20which%20coolers%20ultimately%20made%20this%20guide%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIce%20retention%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EPerhaps%20a%20cooler's%20most%20impactful%20feature%20is%20how%20well%20it's%20able%20to%20keep%20ice.%20Though%20variables%20such%20as%20how%20often%20you%20open%20and%20close%20the%20cooler%2C%20how%20much%20ice%20you%20use%2C%20and%20what%20is%20in%20the%20cooler%20impact%20ice%20retention%2C%20the%20differences%20shouldn't%20be%20so%20dramatic%20that%20you're%20able%20to%20confuse%20a%20poorly%20designed%20cooler%20for%20a%20quality%20one.%20We%20judged%20ice%20retention%20in%20a%20number%20of%20ways%2C%20though%20mostly%20used%20each%20cooler%20as%20we%20normally%20would%20while%20keeping%20track%20of%20how%20much%20ice%20or%20ice%20water%20was%20left%20after%20one%2C%20two%2C%20and%20three%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDurability%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EA%20cooler's%20durability%20comes%20down%20to%20more%20than%20just%20its%20exterior%20quality%20but%20also%20how%20well%20its%20hinges%20or%20zippers%20hold%20up%20to%20constant%20use.%20If%20the%20cooler%20you%20buy%20gets%20a%20lot%20of%20run%20each%20summer%20and%20by%20fall%20you're%20already%20thinking%20you'll%20need%20to%20upgrade%20next%20year%2C%20then%20durability%20is%20a%20major%20concern.%20This%20is%20where%20spending%20more%20money%20on%20a%20premium%20cooler%20can%20save%20you%20quite%20a%20lot%20in%20the%20long%20run.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPortability%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3ECoolers%20are%20inherently%20portable%20(for%20the%20most%20part)%20but%20some%20are%20designed%20far%20better%20than%20others.%20Even%20the%20most%20cumbersome%20of%20coolers%20should%20still%20offer%20some%20method%20for%20it%20to%20be%20easily%20carried%20(via%20one%20or%20two%20people)%2C%20and%20if%20it's%20a%20small%20cooler%20like%20a%20soft%20cooler%20or%20a%20backpack%20cooler%2C%20then%20these%20should%20have%20portability%20near%20the%20top%20of%20what%20list%20of%20what%20they%20do%20exceedingly%20well.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EValue%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EAs%20mentioned%20above%2C%20coolers%20aren't%20always%20an%20inexpensive%20investment%20%E2%80%94%20especially%20the%20premium%20options%20like%20what%20Yeti%20offers.%20But%20if%20you're%20able%20to%20piece%20together%20how%20exactly%20you%20need%20to%20use%20the%20cooler%20and%20for%20wha