ed%20travelers%20than%20myself.%20Over%20the%20last%20year%2C%20I've%20only%20been%20riding%20the%20Amtrak%20between%20New%20York%20City%20and%20New%20England.%20So%20for%20about%20%24130%2C%20I%20can't%20ask%20for%20much%20better.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2249942936-e345-4afd-a825-9227be3a70c3%5C%22%3EManeuvering%20it%20through%20the%20subway%20is%20easy%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20I%20got%20the%20Quince%20carry-on%2C%20I%20was%20using%20a%20two-wheeled%20suitcase%20for%20way%20too%20long.%20The%20360%C2%B0%20turn%20on%20its%20wheels%20really%20makes%20a%20huge%20difference.%20I%20can%20spin%20it%20around%20people%20getting%20on%20and%20off%20the%20subway%20and%20they%20glide%20down%20narrow%2C%20carpeted%20train%20hallways.%20I%20also%20like%20that%20the%20aluminum%20telescopic%20handle%20locks%20into%20a%20halfway%20position%20when%20I%20need%20to%20carry%20it%20up%20the%20platform%20stairs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22425d5828-240b-48da-befa-dbb7d4e64a8d%5C%22%3EIt%20can%20fit%20a%20week's%20worth%20of%20outfits%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20roommate%20used%20this%20exact%20Quince%20carry-on%20on%20a%20weeklong%20trip%20to%20Paris%2C%20and%20it%20fit%20absolutely%20everything%20he%20needed.%20I%20tend%20to%20overpack%20though.%20The%2021-inch%20suitcase%20will%20fit%20me%20about%20six%20days%20worth%20of%20casual%20clothing%2C%20shoes%2C%20and%20toiletries.%20Anything%20extra%20goes%20in%20my%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftravel%2Fbest-travel-backpack%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ebackpack%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20suitcase%20full%20of%20the%20author's%20personal%20belongings.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F682d2472c6ad288d14817bd1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EGabrielle%20Chase%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20compartments%