4000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20exterior%20of%20the%20house%20Collins%20is%20raffling%20off.%3Cp%3EImelda%20Collins%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20a%20lot%20of%20costs%20associated%20with%20the%20raffle.%20I've%20paid%20a%20marketing%20professional%20to%20help%20me%2C%20I've%20run%20national%20ads%20in%20newspapers%20for%20seven%20weeks%2C%20I've%20paid%20for%20a%20photographer%20and%20drone%20videographer.%20Then%2C%20when%20it's%20all%20done%2C%20Raffall%20will%20take%2010%25%20commission%20on%20all%20the%20sales%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20with%20all%20that%2C%20I%20expect%20to%20come%20in%20higher.%20Some%20people%20don't%20understand%20all%20those%20costs%20and%20just%20say%2C%20%26quot%3BOh%2C%20she's%20sold%20150%2C000%20tickets%2C%20so%20she'll%20be%20taking%20in%20%E2%82%AC900%2C000.%26quot%3B%20It's%20not%20that%20simple.%20%3Cem%3E(Editor's%20note%3A%20Collins%20declined%20to%20share%20exactly%20how%20much%20she%20spent%20promoting%20the%20raffle.%20She%20also%20declined%20to%20share%20how%20many%20people%20had%20entered%2C%20but%20as%20of%201%3A30%20p.m.%20ET%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20May%2023%2C%20298%2C624%20paid%20and%20free%20tickets%20had%20been%20issued%2C%20according%20to%20Raffall.)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20laid%20out%20all%20the%20costs%20on%20my%20website.%20I'm%20paying%20for%20the%20legal%20fees%20associated%20with%20the%20transfer%20of%20the%20property%2C%20for%20example.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20yellow%20patio%20table%20with%20orange%20chairs%20sits%20on%20a%20patio%20surrounded%20by%20a%20white%20fence%20with%20the%20Irish%20countryside%20in%20the%20distance%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F682deaf7c6ad288d14818662%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20patio.%3Cp%3EImelda%20Collins%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20want%20the%20winner%20to%20just%2