0familial%20confrontations%20on%20camera.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Ca%20data-tracker%3D%5C%22%7B%26quot%3Barticle_name%26quot%3B%3A%26quot%3BArticle%20Page%20Ad%20Banner%26quot%3B%2C%26quot%3Bposition%26quot%3B%3A1%2C%26quot%3Barticle_id%26quot%3B%3A0%7D%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faarohan.infosys.org%2F%3Fcmpid%3Dsco_TheBetterIndia_EB_AarohanAwards25_foundation_banner_24042025_lq_Awareness_Rgn%5C%22%20data-carousel%3D%5C%22adbanner%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Article%20Ad%20Banner%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2Finfosys-ad-banner-1746535509.jpg%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fa%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2023-year-old%20filmmaker%20from%20Delhi%20has%20already%20begun%20making%20his%20mark.%20%3Cem%3EBabli%20by%20Night%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20his%20debut%20documentary%2C%20has%20been%20longlisted%20for%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bafta.org%2Fmedia-centre%2Fpress-releases%2F2025-bafta-student-awards-longlist-announced%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E2025%20BAFTA%20Student%20Awards%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20documentary%20category%20%E2%80%94%20one%20of%20just%2075%20films%20selected%20from%20over%201%2C000%20submissions%20across%2039%20countries.%20The%20film%20has%20also%20been%20officially%20selected%20for%20the%202025%20New%20York%20Indian%20Film%20Festival%20and%20the%202024%20Rome%20Short%20Film%20Festival.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20next%20day%2C%20I%20reached%20out%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2F_neelsoni%2F%3Fhl%3Den%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENeel%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20invited%20him%20for%20a%20candid%20interview%20with%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fem%3E.%20He%20joined%20in%20along%20with%20his%20film%20e