-to-people%20and%20research%20linkages.%3Cbr%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20framing%20the%20IMBC%20as%20a%20bridge%20across%20Europe%2C%20Africa%2C%20and%20South%20Asia%2C%20India%20is%20catalysing%20a%20new%20model%20of%20corridor-led%20cooperation.%20A%20model%20that%20is%20not%20just%20economically%20viable%20but%20also%20climate-conscious%20and%20innovation-forward.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EBIMSTEC%3A%20Strengthening%20Eastern%20Regionalism%20for%20Shared%20Resilience%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20Confederation%20of%20Indian%20Industry%E2%80%99s%20BIMSTEC%20Business%20Summit%202024%2C%20I%20had%20the%20opportunity%20to%20engage%20with%20high-level%20delegations%20from%20member%20countries%2C%20discussing%20the%20vital%20role%20of%20regional%20collaboration%20in%20addressing%20shared%20challenges.%20Climate%20change%20mitigation%2C%20adaptation%2C%20and%20environmental%20sustainability%20are%20now%20fundamental%20pillars%20within%20BIMSTEC%E2%80%99s%20evolving%20framework%2C%20reflecting%20the%20urgent%20need%20for%20cooperative%20solutions%20across%20borders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Bay%20of%20Bengal%20Initiative%20for%20Multi-Sectoral%20Technical%20and%20Economic%20Cooperation%20(BIMSTEC)%2C%20comprising%20Bangladesh%2C%20Bhutan%2C%20India%2C%20Myanmar%2C%20Nepal%2C%20Sri%20Lanka%2C%20and%20Thailand%20%E2%80%93%20is%20emerging%20as%20a%20key%20platform%20for%20regional%20economic%20integration%20with%20sustainability%20at%20its%20core.%20At%20the%202024%20BIMSTEC%20Business%20Summit%2C%20India%E2%80%99s%20eastern%20engagement%20took%20center%20stage%20as%20member%20nations%20underscored%20their%20collective%20commitment%20to%20climate%20resilience%2C%20clean%20technology%20collaboration%2C%20and%20inclusive%20development%20across%20one%20of%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20most%20climate-vulnerable%20regions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20green%20trade%20facilitation%20and%20eco-tourism%20infrastructure%20to%20nanotech%20for%20clean%20water%20and%20climate%20policy%20coordination%2C%20BIMSTEC%20is%20aligning%20economic%20integration%20with%20environmental%20stewardship.%20As%20one%20of%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20most%20climate-vulnerable%20regions%2C%20this%20collaboration%20offers%20a%20powerful%20model%20for%20shared%20resilience%2C%20knowledge%20exchange%2C%20and%20inclusive%2C%20low-carbon%20growth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20region%20highly%20vulnerable%20to%20climate%20impacts%20such%20as%20rising%20sea%20levels%2C%20extreme%20weather%20events%2C%20and%20biodiversity%20loss%2C%20BIMSTEC%20offers%20a%20platform%20to%20synchronise%20policies%2C%20mobilise%20resources%2C%20and%20share%20knowledge%2C%20strengthening%20collective%20resilience%20and%20sustainable%20development%20goals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20bridging%20national%20priorities%20with%20regional%20strategies%2C%20BIMSTEC%20is%20not%20just%20fostering%20economic%20cooperation%20but%20also%20pioneering%20pathways%20toward%20a%20climate-resilient%20and%20environmentally%20sustainable%20South%20and%20Southeast%20Asia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FTBI-featured-image-2025-05-20T192940.914_11zon-1747749600.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22At%20the%20BIMSTEC%20Business%20Summit%202024%20in%20New%20Delhi%2C%20Dr.%20Ashish%20Sharma%20engaged%20with%20delegates%20from%20Sri%20Lanka%20and%20other%20member%20nations%2C%20exploring%20opportunities%20for%20regional%20cooperation%20and%20development.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FTBI-featured-image-2025-05-20T192940.914_11zon-1747749600.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FTBI-featured-image-2025-05-20T192940.914_11zon-1747749600-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2F