on%5C%22%3EAther%20Energy%E2%80%99s%20listing%20on%20the%20stock%20exchange%20symbolises%20the%20success%20possible%20when%20early%20investors%20back%20long-term%20climate%20innovation.%20Picture%20source%3A%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2Fswapniljain89%2Fstatus%2F1919636042405028185%2Fphoto%2F4%3A%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EX%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20December%202024%20report%20by%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.orfonline.org%2Fresearch%2Ffinancial-and-policy-catalysts-for-climate-tech-expansion-in-india-insights-from-the-green-innovation-and-investment-dialogue%23_edn30%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EObserver%20Research%20Foundation%3C%2Fa%3E%20(ORF)%20stated%20that%20of%20over%202%2C600%20registered%20climate%20tech%20startups%20in%20the%20past%20decade%2C%20only%20about%20800%20are%20active.%20Of%20these%20800%20startups%2C%20only%2025%25%20have%20secured%20funding%2C%20mainly%20in%20the%20seed%20stage%2C%20with%20only%202.5%25%20reaching%20growth-stage%20capital%2C%20mostly%20in%20electric%20mobility.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20why%20is%20it%20important%20for%20India%20to%20fund%20climate%20tech%20startups%3F%20Speaking%20to%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20Gopalika%20Arora%2C%20an%20Associate%20Fellow%20at%20the%20Centre%20for%20Economy%20and%20Growth%20at%20ORF%2C%20notes%20that%20climate%20tech%20plays%20a%20critical%20role%20in%20India%E2%80%99s%20bid%20to%20transition%20away%20from%20fossil%20fuels.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CClimate%20tech%20plays%20a%20very%20critical%20role%2C%20not%20just%20in%20reducing%20emissions%2C%20but%20also%20in%20reshaping%20how%20these%20energy%20systems%20work.%20We%20are%20seeing%20a%20surge%20in%20climate%20tech%20startups%20and%20the%20growing%20ecosystem%20around%20them%2C%20which%20is%20very%20encouraging.%20This%20has%20the%20potential%20to%20foster%20innovation%2C%20promote%20market%20competition%2C%20and%20create%20jobs%20while%20addressing%20deeper%20societal%20challenges.%20In%20a%20developing%20economy%20like%20ours%2C%20this%20makes%20the%20energy%20transition%20not%20just%20greener%20but%20also%20more%20inclusive%20and%20people-positive%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%222400846096%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EMismatch%20in%20investor%20expectations%20and%20startup%20needs%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGiven%20these%20circumstances%2C%20it%20begs%20the%20question%20of%20why%20climate%20tech%20startups%20aren%E2%80%99t%20receiving%20adequate%20and%20long-term%20funding.%20For%20starters%2C%20climate%20tech%20startups%20are%20tough%20businesses%20to%20build.%20They%20are%20very%20capital-intensive%2C%20and%20they%20also%20take%20time%20to%20show%20results.%20Most%20of%20them%20engage%20in%20serious%20investment%20in%20research%20and%20development%20and%20hardware%20just%20to%20get%20out%20of%20the%20laboratory%20and%20into%20the%20real%20world%2C%20whether%20it%E2%80%99s%20electric%20vehicles%20or%20batteries.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGopalika%20argues%20that%20these%20solutions%20demand%20heavy%20upfront%20spending%2C%20and%20in%20recent%20years%2C%20early-stage%20funding%2C%20especially%20at%20the%20seed%20and%20pre-Series%20A%20levels%2C%20has%20become%20more%20accessible%20thanks%20to%20a%20group%20of%20early%20investors%20who%20are%20willing%20to%20take%20a%20bet.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20real%20crunch%20hits%20when%20these%20companies%20try%20to%20scale.%20So%2C%20raising%20money%20on%20Series%20A%20is%20still%20a%20steep%20climb%2C%20and%20without%20that%20capital%2C%20many%20promising%20ventures%20struggle%20to%20grow%20or%20prove%20their%20commercial%20worth.%20The%20problem%20is%20that%20big%20investors%20want%20safe%20bets%20and%20proven%20tech%20like%20solar%20or%20wind.%20But%20startups%20engaged%20in%20next-gen%20climate%20technologies%20like%20green%20steel%20often%20struggle%20to%20attract%20investment%20due%20to%20these%20high%20risks%20and%20long%20gestation%20periods.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%229253875046%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnlike%20software%20or%20any%20other%20asset-light%20businesses%2C%20these%20climate%20tech%20ventures%20require%20substantial%20capital%20at%20very%20early%20stages%20in%20their%20life%20cycle%20and%20need%20more%20time%20to%20break%20even%20and%20scale%20up.%20This%20is%20one%20part%20of%20the%20challenge%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20notes.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20The%20Better%20India%2C%20Gautam%20Das%2C%20the%20CEO%20of%20Oorjan%20Cleantech%2C%20a%20Mumbai-based%20renewable%20energy%20startup%20working%20on%20solar%20solutions%2C%20talked%20about%20the%20challenges%20his%20venture%20experienced%20in%20the%20early%20stages%20while%20seeking%20funding.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CInitially%2C%20we%20approached%20a%20few%20VCs%2C%20held%20some%20healthy%20discussions%2C%20but%20everybody%20was%20just%20in%20a%20hurry%20to%20make%20money%2C%20except%20for%20one.%20By%20mid-2018%2C%20we%20also%20leaned%20into%20our%20network%20of%20family%20and%20friends%20for%20early-stage%20funding%20and%20raised%20about%20Rs%203-4%20crore%20(less%20than%20%24500%2C000).%20We%20have%20not%20raised%20any%20funding%20after%20the%20initial%20seed%20round%2C%20but%20we%20have%20gone%20on%20to%20cross%20Rs%20120%20crore%20in%20revenue%20and%20achieved%20a%20very%20healthy%20%241.5%20million%20EBITDA.%20I%20understand%20that%20you%20may%20not%20last%20without%20money%2C%20you%20may%20not%20scale%20up%20without%20money%2C%20but%20we%20had%20a%20different%20belief%20that%20we%20will%20work%20on%20impact.%20But%20what%20you%20see%20today%20is%20a%20lack%20of%20patient%20capital%2C%20which%20will%20align%20with%20a%20startup%E2%80%99s%20goal%20of%20impact%20and%20purpose%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Gautam.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%227521127830%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FTBI-featured-image-2025-05-19T165247.654_11zon-1747653827.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Oorjan%20Cleantech%20has%20helped%20commercial%20spaces%20like%20the%20Mall%20of%20Dehradun%20adopt%20rooftop%20solar%2C%20despite%20challenges%20in%20securing%20long-term%20investment.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FTBI-featured-image-2025-05-19T165247.654_11zon-1747653827.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FTBI-featured-image-2025-05-19T165247.654_11zon-1747653827-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FTBI-featured-image-2025-05-19T165247.654_11zon-1747653827-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FTBI-featured-image-2025-05-19T165247.654_11zon-1747653827-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F05%2FTBI-featured-image-2025-05-19T165247.654_11zon-1747653827-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-434298%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EOorjan%20Cleantech%20has%20helped%20commercial%20spaces%20like%20the%20Mall%20of%20Dehradun%20adopt%20rooftop%20solar%2C%20despite%20challenges%20in%20securing%20long-term%20investment.%20Picture%20source%3A%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.oorjan.com%2Fstories%2Fa-premier-shopping-mall-in-uttarakhand-pivots-to-green-energy%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EOorjan%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBolstering%20Gautam%E2%80%99s%20point%2C%20Gopalika%20argues%2C%20%E2%80%9CThere%E2%80%99s%20a%20clear%20mismatch%20between%20investor%20expectations%20and%20the%20capital%20needs%20of%20these%20climate%20tech%20ventures.%20Investors%20in%20India%20often%20demand%20that%20startups%20build%20comprehensive%20end-to-end%20value%20chains.%20For%20example%2C%20they%20expect%20e-mobility%20companies%20to%20manage%20everything%20from%20battery%20production%20to%20vehicle%20manufacturing.%20In%20contrast%2C%20China%E2%80%99s%20tech%20ecosystem%20is%20much%20more%20developed%2C%20where%20specialised%20players%20often%20dominate%20different%20segments%20of%20the%20value%20chain%2C%20which%20also%20enables%20a%20company%20to%20focus%20on%20these%20specific%20niches%20and%20innovate%20within%20those%20areas.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20expectation%20of%20broad%20scope%20innovation%20in%20India%20often%20hinders%20the%20more%20targeted%20and%20specialised%20progress%20that%20we%20see%20in%20other%20countries.%20Bridging%20these%20kinds%20of%20gaps%20requires%20very%20enhanced%20collaboration%20between%20the%20investors%2C%20the%20founders%2C%20and%20policy%20makers%20to%20sort%20of%20identify%20certain%20regulatory%20and%20policy%20barriers%20that%20hinder%20green%20capital%20flow%20and%20also%20foster%20a%20more%20conducive%20environment%20for%20scaling%20these%20sustainable%20innovations%20in%20India%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGautam%20also%20notes%20that%20the%20supply%20of%20domestic%20capital%20for%20climate%20tech%20startups%20is%20much%20less%20than%20what%20it%20should%20be.%20It%E2%80%99s%20what%20motivated%20Oorjan%20to%20invest%20in%20such%20startups.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%229669016977%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%E2%80%99s%20a%20shortage%20of%20patient%20capital%20for%20climate%20tech%20startups%2C%20and%20it%E2%80%99s%20a%20gap%20that%20needs%20to%20be%20bridged%20if%20we%20want%20to%20accelerate%20innovation%20in%20this%20space.%20Given%20our%20experience%20and%20the%20consistent%20profits%20over%20the%20last%20six%20years%2C%20we%20felt%20it%20was%20time%20to%20support%20the%20ecosystem.%20We%E2%80%99re%20in%20talks%20with%20a%20few%20startups%20led%20by%20incredibly%20bright%20minds%20working%20on%20impactful%20ideas.%20Our%20approach%20is%20clear%E2%80%94we%E2%80%99re%20offering%20capital%20from%20a%20portion%20of%20our%20profits%2C%20encouraging%20them%20to%20focus%20on%20refining%20their%20proof%20of%20concept%20rather%20than%20chasing%20quick%20returns.%20We%E2%80%99re%20more%20interested%20in%20the%20long-term%20impact%20of%20their%20innovation.%20If%20the%20impact%20is%20real%2C%20the%20income%20will%20follow%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EBuilding%20supporting%20infrastructure%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20second%20issue%20concerning%20the%20lack%20of%20funding%20for%20climate%20tech%20startups%20lies%20in%20the%20availability%20of%20robust%20manufacturing%20infrastructures.%20Climate%20tech%20innovation%20isn%E2%80%99t%20only%20about%20breakthroughs%20in%20science.%20It%20also%20depends%20heavily%20on%20process%20inno